{"search_data": "HaryanaHaryana Youth Job Incentive Scheme for Private Sector Companies Haryana govt. Youth Job Incentive Scheme 2019 for private sector industries, companies to get Rs. 3,000 p.m for 3 years per employee on providing employment to local youths \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Haryana Youth Job Incentive Scheme 2019The state govt. of Haryana wants that all big and medium industries (block A & B) would provide job opportunities to local youths. These companies will be given incentive of Rs. 3,000 for next 3 years on employment of local candidates. This scheme would encourage companies to firstly consider and explore the educational qualification and talent of local candidates.Similar type of scheme is already running in other states like Madhya Pradesh. However there would be no governmental pressure on any company to recruit local youths, this scheme is just for encouragement. The state govt. of Haryana is preparing a separate scheme for this purpose and will implement it soon.In Haryana, there are around 1.2 lakh small and micro enterprises, while the number of big and medium companies is 2415. The total export revenue of these companies is Rs. 89006.17 crore. The new scheme will primarily focus on all big and medium companies.\u0939\u0930\u093f\u092f\u093e\u0923\u0935\u0940 \u092f\u0942\u0925 \u0915\u094b \u0928\u094c\u0915\u0930\u0940 \u0926\u0947\u0917\u0940 \u0907\u0902\u0921\u0938\u094d\u091f\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0924\u094b 3 \u0938\u093e\u0932 \u0924\u0915 3 \u0939\u091c\u093e\u0930 \u0930\u0942\u092a\u090f \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093f \u0915\u0930\u094d\u092e\u0940 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u094b\u0924\u094d\u0938\u093e\u0939\u0928 \u0926\u0947\u0917\u0940 \u0938\u0930\u0915\u093e\u0930 : CM pic.twitter.com/uzU9ULzvzR\u2014 CMO Haryana (@cmohry) August 9, 2019 For the next 3 years, each company will get encouragement amount of Rs. 3000 per month. This means that a company would get Rs. 1,08,000 in the next 3 years for each local employee. The state govt. is also planning to provide other incentives to companies to encourage them to recruit more local youths.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://twitter.com/cmohry  at  "}